            <b>PEOPLE </b> 
          p.content-normal(style="color:#fbfbfb") I am a people person. From a young age, I have had a passion for people and a fascination about their nature. Due to this, I became certified as a coach, so I could look deeper into why people do what they do, why they think how they think, why they react like they do, why they feel what they feel. I published a book about it.

          h5(style="font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.289474em; color: #fbfbfb; padding-right: 25px; ")
            <b>SELLING </b> 
          p.content-normal(style="color:#fbfbfb") The process of convincing somebody that the best choice to satisfy their needs is the one I am offering has fascinated me from a very early age.  Selling gives me the freedom to be myself and use every tool I have to win the battle against my competition. 

          h5(style="font-family: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.289474em; color: #fbfbfb; padding-right: 25px; ")
            <b>COACHING </b> 
          p.content-normal(style="color:#fbfbfb") As a Certified Coach, I help people achieve their goals and/or exceed their limitations by maximizing their inner potential to get the best out of them. It’s not about telling people what to do, it is advising them in their process of change.

 

